headline: Is Emergent’s GSA Contract Expansion Shaping Salesforce’s (CRM) Federal Sector Potential?
summary: Emergent, LLC recently announced it has added Salesforce solutions and services, including the AI-powered Agentforce platform, to its active GSA Contract, enabling federal agencies to more easily procure advanced CRM and workflow technologies through the GSA schedule as of August 7, 2025.
